Right Honourable Paschal Agbodike, Deputy Speaker, Anambra State House of Assembly and member representing Ihiala  constituency 2, has said that the mandate of the All Progressive Grand Alliance (APGA) is to take over South East  zone as a regional political party. The lawmaker in an interview with DAILY INDEPENDENT said that it was wishful thinking for any other political party to think that it would take over leadership of Anambra State in 2021 governorship election in the State. Agbodike maintained that as a party APGA has always put its trust in God. He stressed that at the completion of Governor Willie Obiani’s tenure, the party would have controlled Anambra State for 15 years, pointing out that they did not plan to leave after 15 years. He said that the mandate of the party is to take over the South East region. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! The lawmaker said, “The promise given by our grand patron, late Chukwuemeka Odumegwu Ojukwu, Eze Igbo Gburugburu to South East people is to take over the while of the region. The next election in Anambra State is predetermined by Anambra people, having known that Ndigbo stand for good governance, which  incidentally is what APGA stands for. It is not out of place for other political parties to try to take over the State, they are only trying to exercise their franchise. Anambra is not a one party party State. We have convinced our people on why they should vote for APGA, not only in Anambra State but to also vote out other political parties from the region. APGA is a South East regional party. Other regions have their own regional parties, why not South East.” The Deputy Speaker said that APGA belongs to Ndigbo  and they can get what they have been yearning for through the party. He stressed that the mandate of APGA is all inclusive politics and people should stop being sceptical about the mandate of the party in Anambra. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION